Delete cards from a toucan board
================================

Delete a card which exists
--------------------------

    SCENARIO delete an existing card from a toucan board

    GIVEN    a toucan board
    AND      a card uuid

    WHEN     running "toucan delete card/uuid"

    THEN     the card no longer exists in the store
    AND      the output includes "Deleted card/[:alnum:]"

Attempt to delete a card which does not exist
---------------------------------------------

    SCENARIO delete a card which does not exist

    GIVEN    a toucan board
    AND      a fake uuid

    WHEN     running "toucan delete card/uuid"

    THEN     the output includes "Could not delete card"
